headline.main: Mock Mars Trek Finds Down-To-Earth Sleep Woes

results.snippet: Astronauts have a down-to-Earth problem that could be even worse on a long trip to Mars: They can't get enough sleep. And over time, the lack of slumber can turn intrepid space travelers into drowsy couch potatoes, a new study shows.
